get.description:
Get the latest notifications.

The schema for the *meta* field depends on the notification type:

    identity.validated => meta = null
    identity.rejected => meta = null
    identity.expired => meta = { gracePeriod: <integer> }
    wallet.trx.* => meta = { amount: <string>, currency: <string>, pocketId: <string>, , transactionId: <string> }
